parameters:
\SE\SE[52]It seems you have safely overcome the trial!
\SE[52]You've become noticeably stronger... or so it seems!
\SE[51]There's a different aura surrounding you... or so it
feels!

\SE[6]Hmm! Did you say something about a cat? \SE[16]You seemed
very weak, but now you have a more refined look... or so it
feels!

\SE\SE[20]Huh... Is that so!? \SE[20]Oh no, is it because of the
new foundation...?

\SE[21]Ah, ahaha... \!\SE[5]Cat-san is a rear support role, so
\.I didn't particularly undergo any trials....

\SE[38]Hmm... You seem to have changed. I was confident in my
ability to judge people, but... \SE[56]I wonder... Have you found
a lover or something?

\SE[12]Oh my...? \!\SE[45]I think it's about time for even a
princess like you to exercise your right to remain silent, don't
you think?

\SE[60] (I really hope there won't be any more romantic affairs
within our group...)

\SE[9]Now, Father! \.It is time for a decision!! \!\SE[50]Put an
end to the atrocities of Cordain here and now!!

We have already confirmed the incident in Elmo Village. The
situation has reached a point where we no longer have the luxury
of using indirect means such as proxy wars.

It was confirmed that King Cordain personally took action on-
site... Minister, am I correct?

Yes, there is no mistake. We have also received confirmation from
our spies. The intended purpose is probably...

They are full of youthful vigor.... They probably want to
experience war. ...I am here. If you can stop me, then try to
stop me. That's about it.
This is our mission... or rather...

Let us declare the day after tomorrow as the Day of War!! \!We,
the Ulyssean forces, will mobilize all our troops to put an end
to the atrocities of Cordain!

\SE[16]Father... You have made a great decision!! \SE[52]I will
also go to the battlefield! I will boost the morale of our
soldiers!!

Huh... No, it's not allowed! I always tell you that war is still
too early for you...!

\SE[54]Are you telling me to stay in a safe place while our
country faces a major crisis...!? \!\SE[35]No matter what Father
says, I will go! \!\SE[54]I will deliver a decisive blow to
Cordain with the hammer of justice!!

We do not have any means to stop the princess from becoming like
this...

\SE[2] (Even though it's about to be a decisive battle....
\SE[15] Hehe... This country is really cute.)
\SE[3] (It seems to lack a bit of tension though...)
